OL,3,CHistoric equal pay win for tens of
OL,4,Cthousands of Asda workers
OL,6,FTens of thousands of Asda's checkout
OL,7,Fworkers, customer service staff and
OL,8,Fshop floor assistants, most of whom
OL,9,Fare women, could be in line for
OL,10,Fhistoric payouts after the biggest
OL,11,Fever private sector equal pay claim.
OL,13,FA court ruling has made clear that
OL,14,Fmany of the roles on Asda's shop
OL,15,Ffloors, carried out mainly by women,
OL,16,Fare of "equal value" to the better-
OL,17,Fpaid ones in the supermarket giant's
OL,18,Fwarehouses, which are predominantly
OL,19,Ffilled by men.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
