OL,3,CHistoric equal pay win for tens of
OL,4,Cthousands of Asda workers
OL,6,FThe judges at the Manchester
OL,7,FEmployment Tribunal compared 14
OL,8,Fshopfloor roles to 17 "comparator"
OL,9,Froles carried out in warehouses - all
OL,10,Fof which are better paid.
OL,12,FIt found that in 12 of the roles
OL,13,F"equal value" was established with at
OL,14,Fleast some of the "warehouse
OL,15,Fcolleagues" - and in one case with all
OL,16,Fof them.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
