OL,3,CHistoric equal pay win for tens of
OL,4,Cthousands of Asda workers
OL,6,FHowever, two of the roles did not meet
OL,7,Fthe threshold, and Asda has already
OL,8,Fvowed to take the case to the next
OL,9,Fstage, in which it will argue that
OL,10,Fthere are "material factors" beyond
OL,11,Fsex that explain why they are paying
OL,12,Fthe predominantly male roles a higher
OL,13,Fwage.
OL,15,FMore than 60,000 workers joined
OL,16,Ftogether to accuse the company of sex
OL,17,Fdiscrimination after it emerged that
OL,18,Fthe warehouse workers were earning up
OL,19,Fto #3.74 more per hour.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
