OL,3,CHistoric equal pay win for tens of
OL,4,Cthousands of Asda workers
OL,6,FThe GMB Union and Leigh Day solicitors
OL,7,Fargued that it was an equal pay case
OL,8,Fbecause most of the shop floor workers
OL,9,Fwere women, while the vast majority of
OL,10,Fthose in the warehouses were men.
OL,12,FThe employment tribunal's decision to
OL,13,Fdeclare many of the roles of "equal
OL,14,Fvalue" to the warehouse jobs is a
OL,15,Fmajor step forward for the women - who
OL,16,Fcould be in line for #1.2 billion of
OL,17,Fback-pay and an increased annual pay
OL,18,Fbill of #400 million.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
