OL,4,Cthousands of Asda workers
OL,6,FAs well as checkout operators and
OL,7,Fthose on the customer service desk,
OL,8,Fthe victory covered a number of shop
OL,9,Ffloor assistants, including in
OL,10,Fchilled, the bakery, produce and home
OL,11,Fand leisure departments.
