OL,3,CHistoric equal pay win for tens of
OL,4,Cthousands of Asda workers
OL,6,FThe two roles that were not found to
OL,7,Fbe of equal value were a personal
OL,8,Fshopper (who picks and packs for
OL,9,Fcustomers' online orders) and a shop
OL,10,Ffloor assistant working on "edible
OL,11,Fgrocery".
OL,13,FThe union and its lawyers say they are
OL,14,Fconsidering all available options,
OL,15,Fincluding the possibility of an appeal.
OL,17,FThe result represents a second hurdle
OL,18,Fcleared for the workers who were
OL,19,Fsuccessful in the case.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
