OL,3,CHistoric equal pay win for tens of
OL,4,Cthousands of Asda workers
OL,6,FHowever, the supermarket stressed the
OL,7,Froles that did not win, claiming the
OL,8,Fjudgment had struck out 20% of claims.
OL,10,FThey also pointed out that the judges
OL,11,Fhad used the term "mixed picture" with
OL,12,Fthe other roles. That was because in
OL,13,Fsome cases - "equal value" was
OL,14,Fdeclared with some but not all
OL,15,Fwarehouse roles. However, the lawyers
OL,16,Frepresenting the women say
OL,17,Festablishing "equal value" with any of
OL,18,Fthe warehouse roles is enough because
OL,19,Fall of them are better paid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
