OL,6,FThat leaves Asda needing to establish
OL,7,Fa "material factor" - such as market
OL,8,Fconditions - that demands higher wages
OL,9,Fin the male-dominated part of its
OL,10,Fworkforce.
OL,12,FAn Asda spokesperson said: "We
OL,13,Fstrongly reject any claim that Asda's
OL,14,Fpay rates are discriminatory.
