OL,6,F"Asda will continue to defend these
OL,7,Fclaims at the next stage of the
OL,8,Flitigation because retail and
OL,9,Fdistribution are two different
OL,10,Findustry sectors that have their own
OL,11,Fmarket rates and distinct pay
OL,12,Fstructures."
OL,14,FThe result comes after an email leaked
OL,15,Fto ITV News in the summer of 2023
OL,16,Frevealed that an independent expert,
OL,17,Fwho was commissioned by the court to
OL,18,Fcompare the store workers' jobs to
OL,19,Fthose in the distribution centres, had
OL,20,Fconcluded that the women's roles were
OL,21,Fof equal value.
