OL,6,FNadine Houghton, GMB National Officer,
OL,7,Fsaid: "This is a historic step towards
OL,8,Fsecuring equal pay justice for tens of
OL,9,Fthousands of Asda workers, but it is
OL,10,Ftainted with bitter disappointment for
OL,11,Fthose who now face an appeal.
OL,13,F"These women have been fighting for
OL,14,Fwhat they are owed for more than ten
OL,15,Fyears and are close to ending the era
OL,16,Fof retailers systematically
OL,17,Fundervaluing women.
