OL,6,F"It's telling many of the roles judged
OL,7,Fto be of equal value are the
OL,8,Ftraditional shop floor roles women
OL,9,Fhave held in retail for so long."
OL,11,FBut she admitted it was a "crushing
OL,12,Fblow" for those where the roles were
OL,13,Fnot considered to be equal value,
OL,14,Fwhich could cover up to a third of the
OL,15,Fclaimants.
OL,17,FNevertheless, it is a major victory
OL,18,Ffor tens of thousands of those who
OL,19,Fbrought the case.
