OL,6,F"GMB now calls on Asda to stop wasting
OL,7,Ftime and money dragging this case
OL,8,Fthrough the courts and get round the
OL,9,Ftable with us to agree a settlement,"
OL,10,FMs Houghton said.
OL,12,FLauren Lougheed, Partner at Leigh Day,
OL,13,Fagreed that it was disappointing for
OL,14,Fsome but a major victory for others:
OL,15,F"Equal pay is a fundamental right, and
OL,16,Fthis decision takes us one step closer
OL,17,Fto ensuring that the hardworking
OL,18,Fcolleagues in Asda's stores are not
OL,19,Fundervalued and are paid what they are
OL,20,Fowed.
